# Design Tokens

## Where tokens live

- **Source of truth:** `packages/ui/src/tokens/tokens.json`.
- **Generated CSS variables:** `packages/ui/src/tokens/tokens.css`. Do
  not edit. Imported by `apps/web/src/app/layout.tsx`.
- **Generated TS const:** `packages/ui/src/tokens/tokens.ts`. Do not
  edit.
- **Tailwind theme:** `packages/ui/tailwind.config.ts` exposes tokens as
  utility classes.
- **Generator:** `scripts/generate-tokens.mjs`. Run via
  `npm run tokens:generate`. CI uses `npm run tokens:check`.

## What to use, by need

| Need | Token family | Tailwind |
|------|--------------|----------|
| Page background | `surface.*` | `bg-surface` / `bg-surface-sunken` / `bg-surface-raised` |
| Body / heading text | `text.primary` | `text-text-primary` |
| Muted captions, hints | `text.muted` | `text-text-muted` |
| Primary action / link | `accent.*` | `bg-accent` / `text-accent` |
| Success / danger / warning | `signal.*` | `bg-signal-success` etc. |
| **Personal record only** | `signal.pr` | `text-signal-pr` etc. |
| Card hairlines | `border.subtle` | `border-border-subtle` |
| Form controls | `border.default` | `border-border` |
| Padding | `space.inset.*` | `p-inset-sm`, `px-inset-md` |
| Vertical gaps | `space.stack.*` | `gap-stack-md` |
| Horizontal gaps | `space.inline.*` | `gap-inline-sm` |
| Button/input corner | `radius.control` | `rounded-control` |
| Card corner | `radius.card` | `rounded-card` |
| Pill / avatar | `radius.pill` | `rounded-pill` |
| Focus ring | `--color-focus-ring` | `ring` (DEFAULT) |
| Motion duration | `duration.*` | `duration-fast` / `base` / `slow` |
| Motion easing | `easing.*` | `ease-standard` / `ease-emphasized` |

## Never

- **Never hand-edit** `tokens.css` or `tokens.ts`. Regenerate.
- **Never write raw hex, `px` literal, `rgb()`/`hsl()`** outside L1
  primitives. ESLint will fail your PR.
- **Never write inline `style={}`** outside L1 primitives.
- **Never use Tailwind's default palette** (`bg-gray-100`, `text-red-600`)
  in new code. Always use semantic tokens.

## Adding a token

1. Add to `packages/ui/src/tokens/tokens.json` under the correct layer:
   - `primitive.*` for raw values (rare).
   - `semantic.{light,dark}.*` for new color intents.
   - `semantic.space.*` / `semantic.radius.*` for new sizes.
2. Run `npm run tokens:generate`.
3. Surface in `packages/ui/tailwind.config.ts` if it should be a utility.
4. Document in `design-system/tokens/README.md`.
5. Note in `design-system/changelog.md`.

## Theming

- **Light is default.** Dark is a first-class peer — every semantic token
  has both values.
- **Themes switch via `data-theme="dark"`** on `<html>`. Tailwind's
  `darkMode: ["class", '[data-theme="dark"]']` is already configured.
- **Multi-tenant studios** can override semantic tokens via a scoped
  `data-theme="studio-<id>"` block — primitives don't care.

## Quick sanity check

Before opening a PR with new UI, search your diff for these patterns —
if any match outside L1 primitives, fix before submitting:

```
#[0-9a-fA-F]{3,8}    # hex colors
[0-9]+px              # raw pixel literals
rgb\(|rgba\(|hsl\(|hsla\(   # raw color functions
style={{              # inline styles
bg-gray-|text-gray-|bg-red-|text-red-  # default Tailwind palette
```
